 {"id":"bd-16s.12","title":"Verify roundtrip test coverage for all 14 providers","description":"Verify tests/roundtrip_test.rs covers all 14 providers. Current roundtrip matrix should include: CC, Codex, Gemini, Cursor, Cline, Aider, Amp, OpenCode, ChatGPT, ClawdBot, Vibe, Factory, OpenClaw, Pi-Agent. Check that each provider has at least one round-trip test (write then read-back). If any provider is missing from the matrix, add it. Key invariant: read(write(canonical)) preserves message count, roles, and content text.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-10T17:10:27.150873938Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-10T17:37:14.985874728Z","closed_at":"2026-02-10T17:37:14.985856023Z","close_reason":"Verified: all 14 providers (CC, Codex, Gemini, Cursor, Cline, Aider, Amp, OpenCode, ChatGPT, ClawdBot, Vibe, Factory, OpenClaw, PiAgent) have complete bidirectional roundtrip coverage in tests/roundtrip_test.rs. 110+ roundtrip test functions cover every provider as both source and target. No gaps found.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-16s.12","depends_on_id":"bd-16s","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-10T17:10:27.150873938Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-16s.2","title":"Add Amp provider inline unit tests (writer)","description":"Add inline unit tests for amp.rs write_session() and writer helpers. Tests: (1) writer_roundtrip, (2) writer_thread_id_format, (3) writer_preserves_tool_calls, (4) writer_preserves_tool_results, (5) writer_sets_workspace_env, (6) writer_sets_title, (7) writer_sets_created_timestamp, (8) writer_amp_role_mapping, (9) writer_resume_command. Write to tempdir, read back.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-10T17:07:48.703912848Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-10T17:31:35.909221840Z","closed_at":"2026-02-10T17:31:35.909201041Z","close_reason":"Refactored Amp writer to build_thread_json helper and added inline writer/unit tests for JSON building, role mapping, tool blocks, resume command, plus reader roundtrip.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-16s.2","depends_on_id":"bd-16s","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-10T17:07:48.703912848Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-16s.3","title":"Add Amp provider inline unit tests (detection/helpers)","description":"Add inline unit tests for amp.rs detect(), owns_session(), helpers. Tests: (1) looks_like_thread_id_valid, (2) looks_like_thread_id_invalid, (3) file_uri_to_path_standard, (4) file_uri_to_path_localhost, (5) file_uri_to_path_encoded, (6) provider_metadata, (7) resume_command_format. Note: env var tests need special handling per Rust 2024 set_var rules (see bd-2k0).","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-10T17:07:48.810248699Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-10T17:39:54.845757210Z","closed_at":"2026-02-10T17:39:54.845728947Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-16s.3","depends_on_id":"bd-16s","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-10T17:07:48.810248699Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-16s.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2k0","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-10T17:10:40.858427391Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
